  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/220",
  "title": "API proposal : Remove singleRefine from RefinementList",
  "body": "It seems to me that this parameter is redundant with the menu.\n\nSince the menu is already handling disjunctive + single refine, it is here only for conjunctive faceting.\nWe have two options:\n- If we're considering single value attributes => Then it's already the only refinement displayed\n- If we're considering array attributes => Then why limit the user in his filtering abilities ?\n",
